value:
All is for Lord Duma's sake. Someday
this world, too, shall belong to him.
Heeheehee...

More...about me? There is nothing
more. I have nothing special.
Nothing...

Why do you insist on spending so
much time near me? You are...a
strange one...

Would you accept Lord Duma's
blessing? You'll become more
powerful than you know.$k$pYou'll obtain the power...to destroy
all... Heehee...

I know not of whom, but I sometimes
have...visions...of a familiar face. It's
the face of... Of my...

Your friend
$Nf sends
blessings...$k$pFrom Lord Duma. Heeheehee...

Bow before the might of Lord
Duma!

This shall bring me closer still to
Lord Duma's vision.

I am Lord Duma's faithful servant,
Celica. I shall fill this world...with Lord
Duma's power...

The visions appear as dreams... I see
myself living in a small village... With
an old man and a young boy.$k$pAnd I want...to go there... Yet, I do not
know them or this village. It vexes
me so.$k$pI am certain you are the cause of
these visions... You and the warmth
you have shown me.$k$pWhat was that? You think that
someday...I can go there? Curious...$k$pI am Lord Duma's faithful servant.
And yet... I feel like I might believe
your words...$k$pNo. I mustn't give in.
Alm? Who...who is that? The name is familiar...
If you show me to a field with flowers... I'll make you a wreath...
Aagh, Alm...! Do it now... Kill me!
You are warm... Like a light that pierces the darkness...
